{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"御魂…十七夜…@为了拯救你们，我必须让你们看到这些…","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-1"},{"narration":"因为只是知道我一个人的过去@大概就能体会到好几种悲伤和痛苦了","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-2"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bg":"bg_adv_20021.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":2,"turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story06","nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"就算追溯最初的记忆@我也不记得母亲的容貌","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-3"},{"narration":"我在一间矗立于@散发着潮水香气的城市中的公寓楼里@和忙于工作与玩乐，不怎么回家的爸爸@两人一起生活着","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-4"},{"narration":"我并不觉得自己有那么不幸","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-5"},{"narration":"只要说一声就能拿到餐费@好好学习也能得到表扬","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-6"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21511.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"那时，比起和朋友玩耍@我去图书馆的次数要更多","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-7"},{"narration":"拜次所赐，我比较博学多识@所以周围的人都对我很温柔，生活也很有趣","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-8"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"而且，在学校也没什么问题@虽然外表和其他孩子不同@但同学们都会普通地对待我@所以那个时候大概就是最开心的时光吧","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-9"},{"narration":"所以，要说那个时候的问题@大概就只有穷了@但越是幸福@变得不幸时的落差也更大","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-10"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801200,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":801200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-11"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"骗人的吧…@老师，真的是爸爸吗！？","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"只因为那一件事@一切都急转直下了","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-12"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20761.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"在工作时被冲压机压扁的爸爸@简直令人不忍直视","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-13"},{"narration":"因为最后也没能看见死相@所以最后留下的爸爸的脸的记忆@还是在他死掉的三天前回来时@烂醉如泥的表情","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-14"},{"narration":"喝醉的爸爸会变得很爱撒娇@也会更娇惯我一点@我觉得，留在记忆中的@是可爱的表情真是太好了","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-15"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"但是，从那之后就糟透了","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-16"},{"narration":"因为只剩自己一个人，所以我被送进了孤儿院@听说找到了母亲，我就去见了一面@结果却是个语言不通的大妈","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-17"},{"narration":"虽然不可思议地明白了我们血脉相连@但事到如今，我也不想去一无所知的外国@所以虽然烦恼了一阵，但最后我还是让她回去了","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-18"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21741.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"但是，考虑到那之后经历的事情@说不定飞去外国要好多了@我痛切地感受到，自己实在是@从就读的学校和居住的土地受到了太多恩惠","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-12-19"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[